The paper discusses the integration of smart grid technologies using virtualization and REST APIs, which falls under the domain of networked systems (cs.NI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The proposed architecture also emphasizes re-usability and elasticity, which are key features of software engineering (cs.SE) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper discusses the importance of privacy and security, which is a topic covered in the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
